# Nimbus Design System - Token Rules

**Never hardcode colors, spacing, radii, shadows, or motion values.** Always use Nimbus tokens.

## Colors

| Tailwind utility | CSS variable | Value |
|---|---|---|
| `bg-nimbus-primary` / `text-nimbus-primary` | `--nimbus-primary` | `#1A73E8` |
| `bg-nimbus-primary-hover` | `--nimbus-primary-hover` | `#1666CC` |
| `bg-nimbus-secondary` / `text-nimbus-secondary` | `--nimbus-secondary` | `#5F6368` |
| `bg-nimbus-success` | `--nimbus-success` | `#1E8E3E` |
| `bg-nimbus-warning` | `--nimbus-warning` | `#F9AB00` |
| `bg-nimbus-error` | `--nimbus-error` | `#D93025` |
| `bg-nimbus-surface` | `--nimbus-surface` | `#FFFFFF` |
| `bg-nimbus-surface-subtle` | `--nimbus-surface-subtle` | `#F8F9FA` |
| `border-nimbus-border` | `--nimbus-border` | `#E0E3E7` |
| `text-nimbus-text-primary` | `--nimbus-text-primary` | `#202124` |
| `text-nimbus-text-secondary` | `--nimbus-text-secondary` | `#5F6368` |
| `text-nimbus-text-disabled` | `--nimbus-text-disabled` | `#9AA0A6` |

## Spacing (4/8 scale)

Use `gap-nimbus-{n}`, `p-nimbus-{n}`, `m-nimbus-{n}` utilities, or `var(--nimbus-space-{n})`:

`1`=4px · `2`=8px · `3`=12px · `4`=16px · `5`=20px · `6`=24px · `8`=32px · `10`=40px · `12`=48px · `16`=64px

## Typography

| Scale | Size | Weight | CSS var |
|---|---|---|---|
| Display L | 48px | 700 | `--nimbus-display-l-size` |
| Display M | 36px | 600 | `--nimbus-display-m-size` |
| Headline L | 28px | 600 | `--nimbus-headline-l-size` |
| Headline M | 24px | 600 | `--nimbus-headline-m-size` |
| Title L | 20px | 600 | `--nimbus-title-l-size` |
| Title M | 18px | 600 | `--nimbus-title-m-size` |
| Body L | 16px | 400 | `--nimbus-body-l-size` |
| Body M | 14px | 400 | `--nimbus-body-m-size` |
| Label | 12px | 500 | `--nimbus-label-size` |

Font: `"Google Sans Text", "Noto Sans", "Roboto", Arial, sans-serif` (already set on `body`).

## Radii, Shadows, Motion

```css
/* Radii */
--nimbus-radius-sm: 4px   --nimbus-radius-md: 6px
--nimbus-radius-lg: 8px   --nimbus-radius-xl: 12px

/* Shadows */
--nimbus-shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)
--nimbus-shadow-md: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
--nimbus-shadow-lg: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.10)

/* Motion */
--nimbus-motion-fast: 120ms ease-out
--nimbus-motion-medium: 180ms ease
--nimbus-motion-slow: 240ms ease-in-out
```

## Bad vs. Good

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - hardcoded
<div style={{ color: '#1A73E8', padding: '16px' }} />
<div className="text-blue-600 p-4" />

// ✅ GOOD - Nimbus tokens
<div className="text-nimbus-primary p-nimbus-4" />
<div style={{ color: 'var(--nimbus-primary)', padding: 'var(--nimbus-space-4)' }} />
```
